sections.heading: Reports; department to tabulate
sections.text: The department shall preserve permanently all births, deaths, marriages, and divorces received, and shall tabulate statistics therefrom.SourceLaws 1919, c. 190, tit. VI, art. II, div. IX, ยง 19, p. 785;C.S.1922, ยง 8249;Laws 1927, c. 166, ยง 12, p. 453;C.S.1929, ยง 71-242
